data.description: Nestled within a picturesque landscape, this home boasts stunning curb appeal accentuated by beautiful landscaping. Upon entering the home, a welcoming foyer sets the tone, leading to hardwood floors that gracefully extend throughout the main areas. The residence exudes character with chair rail and crown molding, adding timeless elegance. The kitchen is a focal point, showcasing granite counters and a large pantry, as well as a breakfast room adorned with cathedral ceilings and skylights, inviting abundant natural light. A cozy brick fireplace provides warmth and ambiance, perfect for gatherings. The oversized primary suite offers a retreat, complemented by an attached sitting room that would make a great office. Outside, you can find a large rear deck/patio area, a fenced backyard and detached storage shed. This property harmonizes comfort with sophistication, offering a sanctuary for modern living.
